New poses added for your favourite cannon fodder, now you can make them parade in front of the enemy so they can improve their shooting skills!
Also, apparently the grunts are wasting too much ammo, so here are some reloading poses.

As always, included supported and unsupported versions for each model, you can find one .rar for each group (rifle up, reloading and parading).
Thingivers force to upload at least one STL file, so that guy is just a random pose from the bunch.

Infantry models: https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:3746245
Missile launcher: https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:3782889
Missile launcher and commissar insignia: https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:399182
Chainswords, swords and boltpistols: https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4277183

The troops you send when you want the job done.

There are 120 different poses (44 hellguns, 44 plasma guns and 32 sergeants), only one set (4 x 10) is supported, but it should be really easy to support the others (they are in the .rar files).

Update 2021/10/04: Added a second set (4 units of 10 each), so you can have 2 full formations without repeating a single pose (although the difference may be small xD)

Sources:

Assortment of bases for Epic 40k.

Please note that infantry bases are 40x10 mm or 45x15 mm instead of the traditional 40x12!
Also included 20x20 mm, 25x25 mm and 35x25 mm bases.

All bases are 2mm hight and beveled, holes in the infantry bases are 6 mm wide and 1 mm deep (shallow versions 0.5 mm deep, perfect for BaseDepartment models!)

Update 2020/09/16: Added 45x15 bases and standarized the file names.

Update 2021/01/15: Reuploaded all the files with a raised surface, so they can be printed flat on the bed and removed "easily". No need for supports and much improved precision.

UPDATE 2021/01/19: Added 57! decorated options for the 40x10 shallow bases, with an assortment of rocks and soldier corpses. Sources for these details are:
Rocky Bases - 25mm and 50mm Bases by GoonMasterGames https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4132343
Rock Plateau Tower - JOIN our PATREON by rocket_pig_games http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:3421200

6/8mm Empire Star Army, Acadian Infantry by Miffles_Makes https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:3746245
